'''Zvolen''' ([[jermanikanes]]: ''Altsohl'', [[makyarikanes]]: ''Zólyom'') si yek [[Foro]] ando mashkarutno [[Slovaiko|Slovayko]], pashal i [[Banska Bistrisa]], ko len [[Hron]]. O mashkar le forosko si purano(vi kothe si yek [[khervay]]).

Ando foro si i [[Gandhiskri shkola (Zvolenostar)|Romani Gandhiskri Sikrekher]].

Ando Zvolen sas praxosarde but Romane xelavde.

